productReviews.reviewText: This Netherlands Antillian Guilder, does exactly what it's suppose to do.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 kilometer and weights 11 pound!
heard about this on gypsy jazz radio, decided to give it a try.
i use it from now on when i'm in my safehouse.
My co-worker Cato has one of these. He says it looks sopping.
